A)SOAP
	- simple object access protocol
	- XML based protocol
	- uses:
		a) data transfer
		b) connection between client and server
	- Http request
	- structure:
		a) header
		b) body
		
B) REST
	- representational state transfer
	- JSON based protocol
	- Operations:
		a) Get
		b) Put
		c) Post
		d) delete
	- features:
		a) simple
		b) easy and fast transfer of data
	
B)Testing 
	- code should be written first and then checked.
	- Unit testing
	- Postman
	- Rich client -> Junit
	- REST api -> postman
